{"title":"铁与火颂","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":4,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁与火颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——古巴总理宣布：要用铁与火回击敌人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴是一块铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴是一团火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愤怒的大火烧呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔗刀闪闪地高举。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴是一棵树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棵自由的棕榈树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"片片绿叶都是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢、仇恨、愤怒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肯尼迪那双手上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜血又已经沾满。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁向敌人砍去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火向敌人扑去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界正义的怒涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都向敌人冲去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不可摧毁的自由树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕狂风暴雨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常青的自由树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高唱战斗的歌句。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由树、铁与火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要叫敌人成灰土！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}